Today we're going to look at two of science fiction author Philip K. Dick's best novels with the help of Paul Williams, who was a close friend of Dick's.

12:30.740 --> 12:35.640
That's significant because most of Dick's works first appeared in Paperback, 22 novels in fact.

12:36.140 --> 12:42.500
